Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.47,0:01:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩，厲害\N是寶石嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到彩虹似的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是魔法石也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:02:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?    恩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石降下後30年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類那不屈的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次引導人們\N去建立一個新城市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.99,0:02:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但舊的地區\N現在仍是不幸的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著可怕的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還留下一些廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和先進的米加羅城市相比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是處對比很強烈的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是斜坡，真累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.54,0:02:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會凹凸不平?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隕石啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是30年前隕石的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兒你連這些也不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兒你對以前的事\N不感興趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，看，是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs55\fad(200,200)\pos(480,680)}力量最強!鋼鐵戰士出場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.99,0:03:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電不行，振作點!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再繼續操控下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉，你已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.55,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在難以立足的地方戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用道路雷電是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對\N也可說是某人駕駛得差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我那車子比較安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且雷電的機能也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水面也能走得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管電單車的性能有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管換駕駛的人也會是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛，放手...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找死嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是由我說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因你們常這麼孩子氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以學生才當你們是傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才應該放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我放手\N也不能保證你會放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個比你更加值得信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真會說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了世界，為了人們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以雙手把我幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵戰士，測試開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美夢妮吧，什麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對我們做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣?有意思跟他交手嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是這麼不怕死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達奧羅斯，還差一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.07,0:07:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拿曼達，別著急\N快可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快可以和這達奧羅斯合體了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看，是這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走進這樣的地方嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心腳下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我好等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是猛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來介紹\N這兩位是我的朋友猛和裕一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們會為我們帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶了女孩子來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉和真兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，你帶了額外的電筒來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我一個，我想給他們   恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真兒拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向中間彎曲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在裡面的藥物起了反應\N而射出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼東西向著這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇，逃吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古尼城的地下街?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如發生什麼事便麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想告密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是認為告訴老師會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶?蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享，為何你不一起去?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋寶好像很有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等...我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該更像老師一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們比其他人更擔心大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不老實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是變得像老師嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，好像已經走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怪物火車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂童快出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去的話，可能再來也不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛走，怎會馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點，我快不能呼吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還好好地在呼吸嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.41,0:11:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡有那樣的東西嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是初次見到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽靈火車呀，不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?有入侵者?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達奧羅斯不久便會甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可讓他們接近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮，肯定嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們的下面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是舊地下鐵的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有強烈的妖魔反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以紅外線去找小孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻找到妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮\N小孩們也好像到了地下洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚的看到腳印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.07,0:12:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵，也許現在正和妖魔在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說笑啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如不在被妖魔發現之前找到小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美夢妮，這裡用不到\N我的車子和亮的電單車
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可否使用剛才的鋼鐵戰士?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好提議!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白，立即傳送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK，傳送完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送超音護甲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Borg Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，快去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積克，退後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，喝咖啡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是即溶的，真兒也喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛，你們在這裡生活吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能，我們住在地面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是處很大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一也是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.30,0:15:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用上學也行\N現在也十分快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...父母在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人也在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很晚才會回來，猛的家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小孩完全不關心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不覺得寂寞嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一你在白天一直是獨個兒嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有猛和其他朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.65,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物方面怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天要獨個兒去弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再談這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像莫莉你這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多事情是不會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猛他們喜歡這樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對普通人來說是不能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂童你能明白嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給，咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝\N-真兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.35,0:16:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉，謝謝你替我們擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒想過什麼辛苦或寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相比下\N莫莉你一生不會知道的事、
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體驗到的事，我們卻能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能到學校去也不會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且能為莫莉他們在這裡帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是裕一，了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我老是在亂問些問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介懷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已習慣了被人這樣的去問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.26,0:17:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裕一，是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是初遇見亂童的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也老是在問這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且態度很糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，相比之下\N莫莉還是蠻可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.49,0:17:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-聽到一些聲音\N-哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是幽靈火車嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼地方也好\N你們躲起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快點\N-超音戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.64,0:18:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想是誰，原來是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的正好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這裡變為你們的墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蟑螂似的在洞穴四處出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用子彈來代替殺蟲劑孝敬你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達奧羅斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟沙拿這合體吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積克，別大意，來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看三重怪獸沙拿曼達的英姿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮，小孩們呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下面的地下街躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.13,0:19:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙拿曼達，收拾他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫莉他們的尋寶之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖發生意想不到的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但莫莉他們找到\N比寶物更好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
